  ];
  
  const parseDomain = () => {
    return [
      0,
      Math.max.apply(null, [
        ...data01.map(entry => entry.value),
        ...data02.map(entry => entry.value)
      ])
    ];
  };



export default class Objet2 extends PureComponent {
  static jsfiddleUrl = 'https://jsfiddle.net/shubhi3296/9xopwa9v/3567/';
